# Privacy Policy for Mandala Draw

**Last updated: February 15, 2026**

## Overview
Mandala Draw is a radial symmetry drawing app. Your privacy is important to us.

## Data Collection
Mandala Draw does **not** collect, store, or transmit any personal data, 
usage data, or device information. All drawings are created and stored 
locally on your device only.

## Third-Party Services
This app does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

## Children's Privacy
This app does not collect any data from anyone, including children under 13.

## Contact
If you have questions about this privacy policy, you can contact us at:
[khudaverdian@gmail.com]

## Changes
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be 
posted on this page.
